Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛開始練習騎車帶人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,適應被她抱著可費功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很危險的 不要撓我癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒有撓你癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是輕輕抓住你而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:38.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的腰很怕癢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的手弄得太癢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換個姿勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:44.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太近了 你靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不這樣的話很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 你很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:55.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 靠太近會很熱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不要抱太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明你剛才還說「抓緊了」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來試試看哪種抓法比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你快點 練習的時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,克服了重重困難 終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣就掌握騎車帶人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣就結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:53.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你都掌握了如何騎車帶人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就沒必要繼續特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:02.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你會覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是說你終於鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不寂寞好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要說寂寞感覺會被她捉弄得更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,兩邊都有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學又是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我應該不會寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天去圖書館補作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來對答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:52.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相對的 第二學期要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,颱風真的會來嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,飛得好高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真不愧是颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心裡突然來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風啊 來得更猛烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這感覺 就像是我把風吹起來了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風啊 聽從我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我把頭髮紮起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我剛才看了一下風向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼總在不想被她看見的時候被看見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以說 我在看風向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我還以為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風啊 來得更猛烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定在這樣玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:09.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,客觀來看還真是羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但你為什麼要看風向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是不知道風向會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 畢竟風這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是像這樣把雙手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:30.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 就像是我把風吹起來了一樣 爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家會以為你在這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 我和之前有什麼不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒騎自行車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你覺得我為什麼沒有騎自行車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不告訴別人西片在對著颱風自個兒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都說了那是在看風向…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在那個袋子被吹到這邊之前回答哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有時間限制嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一定要想辦法猜出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,故意問出來 肯定有小心思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:21.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該不是因為風太大騎車危險這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,仔細想想 仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,除了風太大以外 能讓她為難的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自行車 風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是裙子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼害臊的東西怎麼說得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答案是風太大 騎車很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快走吧 該去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總感覺很興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不覺得想要放飛自我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喊著「哇哈哈 風啊 來得更猛烈些吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「我正操縱著疾風」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「現在的我是支配著整個世界的風之王者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「能把學校吹飛到世界的另一端」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哈哈哈哈哈哈哈」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有想那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然不是在看風向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們跑去學校吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼老是那麼狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}感覺今天早上的高木同學 心情非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,馬拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好嘞 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還真是精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不是很討厭跑馬拉松嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 我很期待馬拉松的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 和我一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我贏了 你中午就不許吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒問題 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗跑得超快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我肯定不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要跑馬拉松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明平時連幾十分鐘都沒跑過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼非得去幹這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好像很有幹勁嘛 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的要比嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這可是我提出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:36.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是輸的人要聽勝者命令的比賽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在馬拉松比賽啊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的確感覺他們不像是在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要說正在交往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,多虧了你每天陪我一起訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該是那樣子才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼一定要去跑步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還是死心吧 木村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心無旁騖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 要排除雜念地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為了不浪費體力 一心無二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你上當了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為了這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我連續兩週以上的傍晚都在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不管風吹雨打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 我不可能會輸給她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 專心 專心跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我以為你會沖在更前面的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把握節奏才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來你是不懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你看起來還有餘力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:17.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但肯定是因為看不見我著急得加快腳步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想著讓一下你 剛才都在慢慢地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說她竟然讀懂了我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要沒有午飯吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:43.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我衝得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑那麼快的話 待會肯定會喘不過氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要保持現在的節奏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學很擅長跑馬拉松嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是那樣的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在可不是胡思亂想的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她已經跑回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然有女生跑得比男生還快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然節奏被打亂了 但還是追上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片能碰到我 那就算你贏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:41.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能在眾目睽睽之下去碰高木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣 可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然擾亂了我的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你能和我拉開五十米以上的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就算你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她上鈎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次輪到我來擾亂高木同學的節奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接招吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女生在這裡折返哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}女生在這裡折返
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,男生的折返點還有兩公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都提醒過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂西片 不要停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:40.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 果然會肚子疼 會肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑馬拉松什麼的 哪裡有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是把你抱怨的精力都用在跑步上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就能跑得再快一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不想幹那種沒有意義的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑步和說話 哪邊更沒意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,側腹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也被她捉弄得夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總有一天我會報復回來的 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的側腹真的很怕撓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一有機會就會這樣幹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我的側腹很怕撓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道還有人不怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要來比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,規則是誰先笑誰輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 我準備要說開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:50.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上鈎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你沒有看清局勢啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學正推著自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騰不出雙手 局勢非常不利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這樣子怎麼能保護自己的側腹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的側腹不怕癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇 你忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她竟說自己的側腹不怕癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是在騙我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼她渾身上下都是破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說真的不怕癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之只要試一試就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺好害臊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以戳她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會不會被當做是性騷擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不上的話 又輪到我進攻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還覺得是個完美的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到還有這樣的陷阱在裡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風險太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在應該和她保持距離 算作平局好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:43.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你的表情太犯規了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你笑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學還有鬼臉這一必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要讓你幹什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 還有懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是當然的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一輩子不許吃大米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,禁止看百分百單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣好像也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你戳我的側腹看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就是懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:03.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她是打算讓我害羞不敢碰她來取樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不會讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:15.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說 我好像還是第一次去碰高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不要想無關的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要戳她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:34.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯吧 我側腹不怕癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,腋下倒是很怕癢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰敢碰那種地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:02.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好了 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假時沒去試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放學的時候去一趟吧 不去不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是靈異地點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的要進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不是參加試膽大會的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是油桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全不嚇人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎 難道不嚇人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是飛盤 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像好涼快 是不是鬼怪作祟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是白天比較通風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不要追著我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們玩夠沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,非常有暑假的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假已經一去不復返了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別突然就低沉下來啊 真煩人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.04,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:25.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:42.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:06.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:14.98,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:20.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:34.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.04,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:25.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:42.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:06.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:14.98,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:20.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:34.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って努力は嫌いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.86,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って人は人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ窓ガラスに映る姿気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.24,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ意地になって　移る流行気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言ってお伽話は罠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.84,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}期待したってカボチャはカボチャ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.68,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:59.02,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走り出した足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:07.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも抜かれたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.96,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも負けたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:26.38,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}說實話 我最討厭的就是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.86,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}說實話 別人就是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但為什麼我會在意自己映在玻璃窗上的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.24,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但為什麼意氣用事地在意著不斷變化的流行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}說實話 童話故事都是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.84,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就算如何期待 南瓜也還是南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.68,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有點不行了 感覺最近的自己有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:59.02,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有點不行了 感覺最近的自己有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.73,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}疾馳的腳步無法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:07.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那個人的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望被任何人超越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒 風兒 助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}腳步無法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那個人的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:26.38,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒 風兒 助我一臂之力
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
